Has your primary care doctor or insurance changed?

If so, call financial coordination at 617-636-6013 to ensure we have your updated insurance information.

/* What it does: A work-around for email clients meddling in triggered links. */
/* What it does: Prevents Gmail from displaying an download button on large, non-linked images. */
/* If the above doesn't work, add a .g-img class to any image in question. */
/* What it does: Prevents underlining the button text in Windows 10 */

/* What it does: Remove spaces around the email design added by some email clients. */
/* Beware: It can remove the padding / margin and add a background color to the compose a reply window. */
/* What it does: Stops email clients resizing small text. */
/* What it does: Centers email on Android 4.4 */
/* What it does: Stops Outlook from adding extra spacing to tables. */
/* What it does: Fixes webkit padding issue. Fix for Yahoo mail table alignment bug. Applies table-layout to the first 2 tables then removes for anything nested deeper. */
/* What it does: Uses a better rendering method when resizing images in IE. */
/* What it does: A work-around for email clients meddling in triggered links. */
/* What it does: Prevents Gmail from displaying an download button on large, non-linked images. */
/* If the above doesn't work, add a .g-img class to any image in question. */
/* What it does: Prevents underlining the button text in Windows 10 */
/* What it does: Removes right gutter in Gmail iOS app: https://github.com/TedGoas/Cerberus/issues/89  */
/* Create one of these media queries for each additional viewport size you'd like to fix */
/* Thanks to Eric Lepetit (@ericlepetitsf) for help troubleshooting */
@media only screen and (min-device-width: 375px) and (max-device-width: 413px) { /* iPhone 6 and 6+ */

/* What it does: Remove spaces around the email design added by some email clients. */
/* Beware: It can remove the padding / margin and add a background color to the compose a reply window. */
/* What it does: Stops email clients resizing small text. */
/* What it does: Centers email on Android 4.4 */
/* What it does: Stops Outlook from adding extra spacing to tables. */
/* What it does: Fixes webkit padding issue. Fix for Yahoo mail table alignment bug. Applies table-layout to the first 2 tables then removes for anything nested deeper. */
/* What it does: Uses a better rendering method when resizing images in IE. */
/* What it does: A work-around for email clients meddling in triggered links. */
/* What it does: Prevents Gmail from displaying an download button on large, non-linked images. */
/* If the above doesn't work, add a .g-img class to any image in question. */
/* What it does: Prevents underlining the button text in Windows 10 */
/* What it does: Removes right gutter in Gmail iOS app: https://github.com/TedGoas/Cerberus/issues/89  */
/* Create one of these media queries for each additional viewport size you'd like to fix */
/* Thanks to Eric Lepetit (@ericlepetitsf) for help troubleshooting */
@media only screen and (min-device-width: 375px) and (max-device-width: 413px) { /* iPhone 6 and 6+ */

/* What it does: Remove spaces around the email design added by some email clients. */
/* Beware: It can remove the padding / margin and add a background color to the compose a reply window. */
/* What it does: Stops email clients resizing small text. */
/* What it does: Centers email on Android 4.4 */
/* What it does: Stops Outlook from adding extra spacing to tables. */
/* What it does: Fixes webkit padding issue. Fix for Yahoo mail table alignment bug. Applies table-layout to the first 2 tables then removes for anything nested deeper. */
/* What it does: Uses a better rendering method when resizing images in IE. */
/* What it does: A work-around for email clients meddling in triggered links. */
/* What it does: Prevents Gmail from displaying an download button on large, non-linked images. */
/* If the above doesn't work, add a .g-img class to any image in question. */
/* What it does: Prevents underlining the button text in Windows 10 */
/* What it does: Removes right gutter in Gmail iOS app: https://github.com/TedGoas/Cerberus/issues/89  */
/* Create one of these media queries for each additional viewport size you'd like to fix */
/* Thanks to Eric Lepetit (@ericlepetitsf) for help troubleshooting */
@media only screen and (min-device-width: 375px) and (max-device-width: 413px) { /* iPhone 6 and 6+ */

Finish the remaining half of the solution at least 5 hours before your procedure.

/* What it does: Remove spaces around the email design added by some email clients. */
/* Beware: It can remove the padding / margin and add a background color to the compose a reply window. */
/* What it does: Stops email clients resizing small text. */
/* What it does: Centers email on Android 4.4 */
/* What it does: Stops Outlook from adding extra spacing to tables. */
/* What it does: Fixes webkit padding issue. Fix for Yahoo mail table alignment bug. Applies table-layout to the first 2 tables then removes for anything nested deeper. */
/* What it does: Uses a better rendering method when resizing images in IE. */
/* What it does: A work-around for email clients meddling in triggered links. */
/* What it does: Prevents Gmail from displaying an download button on large, non-linked images. */
/* If the above doesn't work, add a .g-img class to any image in question. */
/* What it does: Prevents underlining the button text in Windows 10 */
/* What it does: Removes right gutter in Gmail iOS app: https://github.com/TedGoas/Cerberus/issues/89  */
/* Create one of these media queries for each additional viewport size you'd like to fix */
/* Thanks to Eric Lepetit (@ericlepetitsf) for help troubleshooting */
@media only screen and (min-device-width: 375px) and (max-device-width: 413px) { /* iPhone 6 and 6+ */

/* What it does: Remove spaces around the email design added by some email clients. */
/* Beware: It can remove the padding / margin and add a background color to the compose a reply window. */
/* What it does: Stops email clients resizing small text. */
/* What it does: Centers email on Android 4.4 */
/* What it does: Stops Outlook from adding extra spacing to tables. */
/* What it does: Fixes webkit padding issue. Fix for Yahoo mail table alignment bug. Applies table-layout to the first 2 tables then removes for anything nested deeper. */
/* What it does: Uses a better rendering method when resizing images in IE. */
/* What it does: A work-around for email clients meddling in triggered links. */
/* What it does: Prevents Gmail from displaying an download button on large, non-linked images. */
/* If the above doesn't work, add a .g-img class to any image in question. */
/* What it does: Prevents underlining the button text in Windows 10 */
/* What it does: Removes right gutter in Gmail iOS app: https://github.com/TedGoas/Cerberus/issues/89  */
/* Create one of these media queries for each additional viewport size you'd like to fix */
/* Thanks to Eric Lepetit (@ericlepetitsf) for help troubleshooting */
@media only screen and (min-device-width: 375px) and (max-device-width: 413px) { /* iPhone 6 and 6+ */

/* What it does: Uses a better rendering method when resizing images in IE. */
/* What it does: A work-around for email clients meddling in triggered links. */

/* If the above doesn't work, add a .g-img class to any image in question. */
/* What it does: Prevents underlining the button text in Windows 10 */

/* Create one of these media queries for each additional viewport size you'd like to fix */
/* Thanks to Eric Lepetit (@ericlepetitsf) for help troubleshooting */

/* What it does: Remove spaces around the email design added by some email clients. */
/* Beware: It can remove the padding / margin and add a background color to the compose a reply window. */
/* What it does: Stops email clients resizing small text. */
/* What it does: Centers email on Android 4.4 */
/* What it does: Stops Outlook from adding extra spacing to tables. */
/* What it does: Fixes webkit padding issue. Fix for Yahoo mail table alignment bug. Applies table-layout to the first 2 tables then removes for anything nested deeper. */
/* What it does: Uses a better rendering method when resizing images in IE. */
/* What it does: A work-around for email clients meddling in triggered links. */
/* What it does: Prevents Gmail from displaying an download button on large, non-linked images. */
/* If the above doesn't work, add a .g-img class to any image in question. */
/* What it does: Prevents underlining the button text in Windows 10 */
/* What it does: Removes right gutter in Gmail iOS app: https://github.com/TedGoas/Cerberus/issues/89  */

/* Thanks to Eric Lepetit (@ericlepetitsf) for help troubleshooting */

/* What it does: Remove spaces around the email design added by some email clients. */
/* Beware: It can remove the padding / margin and add a background color to the compose a reply window. */
/* What it does: Stops email clients resizing small text. */
/* What it does: Centers email on Android 4.4 */
/* What it does: Stops Outlook from adding extra spacing to tables. */
/* What it does: Fixes webkit padding issue. Fix for Yahoo mail table alignment bug. Applies table-layout to the first 2 tables then removes for anything nested deeper. */
/* What it does: Uses a better rendering method when resizing images in IE. */
/* What it does: A work-around for email clients meddling in triggered links. */
/* What it does: Prevents Gmail from displaying an download button on large, non-linked images. */
/* If the above doesn't work, add a .g-img class to any image in question. */
/* What it does: Prevents underlining the button text in Windows 10 */
/* What it does: Removes right gutter in Gmail iOS app: https://github.com/TedGoas/Cerberus/issues/89  */
/* Create one of these media queries for each additional viewport size you'd like to fix */
/* Thanks to Eric Lepetit (@ericlepetitsf) for help troubleshooting */
@media only screen and (min-device-width: 375px) and (max-device-width: 413px) { /* iPhone 6 and 6+ */
